WEBVTT

00:03:58.592 --> 00:04:01.052
But we convinced him
to start collaborating

00:04:01.076 --> 00:04:02.928
with the Congo Basin Institute.

00:04:02.952 --> 00:04:07.569
Today, his lab in Buea
has over half a dozen collaborative grants

00:04:07.593 --> 00:04:10.167
with researchers from the US and Europe

00:04:10.191 --> 00:04:13.752
supporting 14 graduate students,
nine of them women,

00:04:13.776 --> 00:04:15.792
all carrying out groundbreaking research

00:04:15.816 --> 00:04:18.221
understanding biodiversity
under climate change,

00:04:18.245 --> 00:04:19.649
human health and nutrition.

